  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a city skyline reflected on calm water. A long bridge with glowing lights stretches across the water, connecting the city to distant land. The city itself is a dazzling display of lights, featuring high-rise buildings and structures illuminated in various colors. Dominating the skyline is a particularly tall building with a bright, colorful light display at the top. The surrounding hills are visible in the background, adding depth to the scene. Long streaks of light suggest moving traffic on the bridge and possibly on the water.",
